headline: A Look At CF Industries (CF) Valuation As Low Carbon Fertilizer Pilot With POET Gains Traction
summary: CF Industries Holdings (CF) is back in focus after launching a low carbon fertilizer pilot with POET and several farm cooperatives, aiming to cut the carbon intensity of corn and support lower carbon ethanol production. See our latest analysis for CF Industries Holdings.
